PrecisEnactment of the NEW BRUNSWICK PRIMARY FOREST PRODUCTS ORDER - which authorizes a number of marketing boards in New Brunswick to regulate the marketing of primary forest products in interprovincial and export trade, and to fix, impose and collect levies or charges in order to finance their operations.
